{"identifier":{"interfaceLanguage":"swift","url":"doc:\/\/GLibObject\/documentation\/GLibObject\/InitiallyUnownedRef\/onNotify(flags:handler:)"},"schemaVersion":{"patch":0,"minor":3,"major":0},"sections":[],"abstract":[{"type":"text","text":"The notify signal is emitted on an object when one of its properties has"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"its value set through "},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"g_object_set_property()"},{"text":", ","type":"text"},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"g_object_set()"},{"text":", et al.","type":"text"}],"primaryContentSections":[{"declarations":[{"platforms":["macOS"],"tokens":[{"text":"@discardableResult","kind":"attribute"},{"text":" ","kind":"text"},{"text":"func","kind":"keyword"},{"text":" ","kind":"text"},{"text":"onNotify","kind":"identifier"},{"text":"(","kind":"text"},{"text":"flags","kind":"externalParam"},{"text":": ","kind":"text"},{"preciseIdentifier":"s:10GLibObject12ConnectFlagsV","kind":"typeIdentifier","text":"ConnectFlags","identifier":"doc:\/\/GLibObject\/documentation\/GLibObject\/ConnectFlags"},{"kind":"text","text":" = ConnectFlags(0), "},{"kind":"externalParam","text":"handler"},{"text":": ","kind":"text"},{"text":"@escaping","kind":"keyword"},{"kind":"text","text":" ("},{"text":"ObjectRef","identifier":"doc:\/\/GLibObject\/documentation\/GLibObject\/ObjectRef","preciseIdentifier":"s:10GLibObject0B3RefV","kind":"typeIdentifier"},{"text":", ","kind":"text"},{"kind":"typeIdentifier","identifier":"doc:\/\/GLibObject\/documentation\/GLibObject\/ParamSpecRef","preciseIdentifier":"s:10GLibObject12ParamSpecRefV","text":"ParamSpecRef"},{"kind":"text","text":") -> "},{"kind":"typeIdentifier","preciseIdentifier":"s:s4Voida","text":"Void"},{"kind":"text","text":") -> "},{"kind":"typeIdentifier","preciseIdentifier":"s:Si","text":"Int"}],"languages":["swift"]}],"kind":"declarations"},{"kind":"parameters","parameters":[{"content":[{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"text":"Flags","type":"text"}]}],"name":"flag